section.section:
The Mortgage Loan Servicing Practices Settlement Fund shall be used for housing and foreclosure-relief purposes and for related investigation and enforcement activities, including:
the provision of housing counseling;
legal assistance related to foreclosure and housing activities;
criminal or civil investigations of fraud related to housing and the securitization of mortgage loans;
relevant enforcement activities;
foreclosure prevention, remediation, and restitution;
programs to address community blight;
programs reasonably targeted to benefit persons harmed by mortgage fraud; and
any other public purpose reasonably related to housing and foreclosure relief.
